query.name: DecompositionQueryOnInterface
query.sql: SELECT i.* FROM design_moduleinterface i JOIN design_realizerelation r ON i.`fact-id`=r.child AND i.version=r.version JOIN __versions__ v ON i.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND r.parent=$ParentFactId

query.name: DecompositionQueryOnModule
query.sql: SELECT m.* FROM design_module m JOIN design_modulerefinementrelation d ON m.`fact-id`=d.child AND m.version=d.version JOIN __versions__ v ON m.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.parent=$ParentFactId

query.name: DecompositionRelationQuery
query.sql: SELECT d.* FROM design_modulerefinementrelation d JOIN __versions__ v ON d.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.parent=$ParentFactId AND d.child=$ChildFactId

query.name: DependencyQueryOnInterface
query.sql: SELECT i.* FROM design_moduleinterface i JOIN design_moduledependencyrelation d ON i.`fact-id`=d.child AND i.version=d.version JOIN __versions__ v ON i.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.parent=$ParentFactId

query.name: ReverseDependencyQueryOnInterface
query.sql: SELECT i.* FROM design_moduleinterface i JOIN design_moduledependencyrelation d ON i.`fact-id`=d.parent AND i.version=d.version JOIN __versions__ v ON i.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.child=$ChildFactId

query.name: DependencyQueryOnModule
query.sql: SELECT m.* FROM design_module m JOIN design_moduledependencyrelation d ON m.`fact-id`=d.child AND m.version=d.version JOIN __versions__ v ON m.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.parent=$ParentFactId

query.name: ReverseDependencyQueryOnModule
query.sql: SELECT m.* FROM design_module m JOIN design_moduledependencyrelation d ON m.`fact-id`=d.parent AND m.version=d.version JOIN __versions__ v ON m.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.child=$ChildFactId

query.name: DependencyRelationQuery
query.sql: SELECT d.* FROM design_moduledependencyrelation d JOIN __versions__ v ON d.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND d.parent=$ParentFactId AND d.child=$ChildFactId

query.name: ModuleFactIDsQuery
query.sql: SELECT m.* FROM design_module m JOIN __versions__ v ON m.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName

query.name: RealizationRelationQuery
query.sql: SELECT r.* FROM design_realizerelation r JOIN __versions__ v ON r.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND r.parent=$ParentFactId AND r.child=$ChildFactId

query.name: RootModuleInterfaceQuery
query.sql: SELECT m.* FROM design_moduleinterface m JOIN __versions__ v ON m.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND `fact-id`=$ParentFactId

query.name: RootModuleQuery
query.sql: SELECT m.* FROM design_module m JOIN __versions__ v ON m.version=v.id WHERE version_name=$VersionName AND `fact-id`=$ParentFactId

query.name: VersionIDQuery
query.sql: SELECT v.ID FROM __versions__ v WHERE v.version_name=$VersionName

query.name: VersionNamesQuery
query.sql: SELECT v.ID, v.version_name, v.date_created, v.storage_type, v.factSet, v.parent FROM __versions__ v
